WEBVTT

00:09:30.163 --> 00:09:34.497
And maybe we scold, and maybe
we hold back an incentive or two.

00:09:34.521 --> 00:09:36.473
But you know what the best incentive is?

00:09:36.497 --> 00:09:37.670
A job.

00:09:37.694 --> 00:09:39.769
And you know what
the best disincentive is?

00:09:39.793 --> 00:09:41.034
Losing it.

00:09:41.058 --> 00:09:44.793
So if companies really
want accountability,

00:09:44.817 --> 00:09:46.922
they should assume that that is a given.

00:09:46.946 --> 00:09:51.180
Consequences are what happen when you
don't do what you're accountable for.

00:09:52.426 --> 00:09:54.414
Imagine this:

00:09:54.438 --> 00:10:01.189
imagine a place where people
of all colors and all races